{"type": "article", "id": 21977, "title": "nendo 星战周边", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-05T08:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021257174WTzKGavCegOADLJ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是 Nendo 推出的星球大战周边，他们以球体为基础，制作了不同的人物造型。简化后的形象只保留了最具识别度的元素，表面有凹凸纹理或附加的配件，小巧可爱。这种模块化的设计可以被运用在很多领域，首饰挂坠，小玩具，餐具如调料盒。它的有趣的延展是 nendo 的一种探索。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/star-wars-2/?erelease\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125714DX2WQrNagVUTtb0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125715yVNMB3dmf6kiOovY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125715QH3sLecaPSBlhmiG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021257169vLXOr7USGcVdqhu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212571670EkwcDBeYiNpIMQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}